		<td><b>blinking powerpak !!! Please help with question! reset !</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Please help with question!
<br />
<br />I just got my powerpak from retro zone when i first put it in it kept blinking on and off changed the 72 pin connector same thing then i decided to hold down reset and now works fine everytime after that anyone know why??? did it have to sync to a region or some other odd
<br />reason or create a file by holding reset???

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
